<body style="tab-interval:21pt;text-justify-trim:punctuation;" ><!--StartFragment--><div class="Section0"  style="layout-grid:15.6000pt;" ><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-align:center;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,0);mso-highlight:rgb(255,255,0);" ><font face="等线" >可以聚会了吗？看看模型怎么说！</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;background:rgb(255,255,0);mso-highlight:rgb(255,255,0);" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >在武汉封城</font>56天以后，我们终于迎来了包括武汉在内的境内传播零增长！</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >全国的工作重心逐渐转至防控境外输入病例</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >。全面复工复学在望。经过了漫长的冬天，我们是不是可以摘掉口罩，长舒一口气，聚一聚久违的朋友了？</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >就在此时，传来哈尔滨检测到一位境外输入的毫无症状的带病毒者，不发烧，不咳嗽，神清气明，自我感觉良好。若不是入境的全面隔离和核算检测，完全发现不了！</font></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >在复工复学的人群中会不会有这样的隐形带毒者，他们的传播风险有多大呢？</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >我们设计了一个</font></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >可交互的蒙特卡洛仿真模型</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，针对这种情况，通过模型和数据告诉你一个病毒携带者将带来多大的影响，防控的措施有多重要。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=23  style="margin-left:42.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#108;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >严格防控措施下日常生活风险较小</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-left:21.0000pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >疫情的有效抑制得益于全面隔离，当社会开始全面复工复学时，人员的流动增加，人员聚集度会发生较大变化。在我们的模型里，</font>&nbsp;<font face="等线" >按照密切接触者为持续接触一小时以上的定义，将模型中人员聚集度定为</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >8</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >人；考虑戴口罩、消毒等严格防护措施，病毒传染率类似全面隔离状态；假设复工期间仍保持严格的排查措施，具有充足的医疗能力，即患者出现症状的当天立即能得到收治，将模型中从发病到收治间隔取为</font>1天。经过仿真，由一个病毒携带者所引起的累计疫情预测曲线和新增疫情预测曲线如图1和图2所示。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-align:center;" ><img width="830"  height="450"  src="static/single-img/一个病毒携带者的影响-3.21535.png" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-align:center;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >图</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >1&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >人员聚集度较小情况下的累计疫情预测（严格防控）</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-align:center;" ><img width="832"  height="378"  src="static/single-img/一个病毒携带者的影响-3.21564.png" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-align:center;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >图</font>2</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >人员聚集度较小情况下的新增疫情预测（严格防控）</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-align:center;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >从以上</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >仿真曲线</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >可以看出</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，</font></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >复工期间若出现一个病毒携带者</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >严格的防控措施</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，包括及时</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >确诊</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >、</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >及时隔离</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >密切接触者等，</font></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >可以减缓病毒的进一步传播，累计确诊人数可以控制在几十人的范围，</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >3-4月</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >后</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >疫情</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >可以</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >完全</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >清</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >除</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >。</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=23  style="margin-left:42.0000pt;text-indent:-21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:0.0000;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span sty