-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，例如出现不带口罩、政府不再追踪确诊患者的密切接触者等情况，</font></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >即使在复工过程中只有一个感染者，模型预测病毒依然会在</font>2-3个月后重新开始爆发</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >疫情预测曲线</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >如</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >图</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >7</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >和图</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >8。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >这正是在世界多国在重演的悲剧。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-align:center;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-f