b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >我们调研了各省市人民政府、卫生健康委员会、疾病预防控制中心等部门所公布的疫情文件，使用黑龙江、吉林等</font>1</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >5</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >个省市有关密切接触者、累计确诊人数等数据，假设潜伏期</font>Te=</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >4</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，发病到确诊时间</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >Tq从1到5取值时，依据下述公式：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  align=center  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-align:center;" ><img width="202"  height="94"  src="static/single-img/一个病毒携带者的影响-3.212369.png" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-align:left;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000p