线" >（发病到确诊</font>1天）。</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >考虑到戴口罩、消毒等各种防护措施对传染能力的影响，可将传染率</font>&#946;减小至0</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >.06</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&#946;。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >（</font>2）人员聚集度m的确定</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >复工复学人群可分为中小学复学人群、大学复学人群、复工人群三类；人员聚集度</font>m指的是平均每人每天接触的人数，</span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >针对每类人群而言，是否错峰就餐、错峰上下班、上下学等防控措施均对</font>m值产生影响。</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=MsoNormal ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >（</font>3）</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:等线;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >病毒潜伏天数</font>Te</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-ascii-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-hansi-font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >的确定</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >基于目前的流行病学调查和研究结果，潜伏期为</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >1-14&nbsp;天，多为&nbsp;3-7&nbsp;天；</span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >我们设定</font>Te在</span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" >1-14内符合一定概率分布</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;" ><font face="等线" >，</font>Te=12-14的概率为0.05，Te=7-11的概率为0.03，Te=3-6的概率为0.15，Te=1-2的概率为0.05&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:等线;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:10.5000pt;m